subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/User
object: A user (agent, person, group or organization) of a PGP/GPG public key.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/
object: Web Of Trust (wot) RDF vocabulary, described using W3C RDF Schema and the Web Ontology Language.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/PubKey
object: A class used to represent a PGP/GPG public key for a user (an agent, person, group or organization).

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/hasKey
object: A property to link a PubKey from a User

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/signer
object: A property linking a public key signature event to the public key that was used to sign.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/EncryptedDocument
object: An encrypted document intended for a set of recipients.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/sigdate
object: The date of a public key signature event.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/encrypter
object: A property linking an encrypted document to the public key that was used to encrypt it.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/fingerprint
object: A public key hex fingerprint string (40 digits, white space insignificant).

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/length
object: A numeric string representing the length, in bytes, of a public key.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/signed
object: A property linking a public key to a public key signature event.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/identity
object: A property linking a public key to the user of the key.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/pubkeyAddress
object: The location of an ascii version of a public key.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/sigtime
object: The time (of day) of a public key signature event.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/assurance
object: A property linking a document to an endorsement resource containing a detached ascii signature.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/hex_id
object: A public key hex identifier string (8 digits).

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/SigEvent
object: An event describing the action of a public key being signed by some other public key.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/encryptedTo
object: A property linking an encrypted document to a recipient.

subject: http://xmlns.com/wot/0.1/Endorsement
object: An endorsement resource containing a detached ascii signature.
